  "title": "Events Sales and Marketing (Travel Opportunities + Fun and Progressive Environment!)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></h2><h3>🎯 A simple choice TODAY could change your tomorrow!</h3><p>💯 We’re not looking for perfect—just someone ready to GROW.<br /><strong>“Talent is transferable. Bring the drive, we’ll provide the tools.”</strong></p><h2>🌍 <strong>Who We Are</strong></h2><p>At <strong>Rezolute Globalz</strong>, we partner with leading brands across lifestyle, tech, and charity sectors through events and marketing campaigns. We engage with people, build brand awareness, and create meaningful impact.</p><p>Beyond what we do, we focus on who we become.<br />Our culture is built on <strong>growth, mentorship, confidence, leadership, and resilience</strong>.</p><h2>🎁 <strong>What You’ll Get</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Full training and personalised mentorship</p></li><li><p>Local and international travel opportunities</p></li><li><p>A supportive, high-energy team environment</p></li><li><p>Real-world experience that builds communication, confidence, and people skills</p></li></ul><h2>🧠 <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Strong communication and people skills</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn, grow, and take on challenges</p></li><li><p>Consistent, disciplined, and reliable attitude</p></li><li><p>A team player who thrives in a dynamic environment</p></li></ul><h2>💼 <strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Represent brands at events and marketing campaigns</p></li><li><p>Engage customers and share meaningful brand stories</p></li><li><p>Support planning and on-ground team activities</p></li><li><p>Develop leadership capabilities with growth pathways available</p></li></ul><p><em></em></p>",
